rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Your Majesty...
are you sure about searching
for the boy yourself?

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0003
rows.name:
The Heaven's Holy Grail is throwing
all of Alst into chaos right now.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0004
rows.name:
And only another Heaven's Holy Grail
can stand against it.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0005
rows.name:
It's possible our country
can't deal with this alone.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0006
rows.name:
So you're saying it's in Superbia's
best interest to work with them.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0009
rows.name:
If you don't want to bother His Majesty,
then we should just take the initiative.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0011
rows.name:
Then shall we eagerly head for
the camp said to be in
the Seigle Hills?
